02:32.733 --> 02:34.200
you had to swim
a mile and a half

02:34.267 --> 02:36.300
through the icy waters
of San Francisco Bay.

02:36.567 --> 02:38.700
Yeah, plus, add the fact
that the brothers don't swim.

02:38.833 --> 02:39.867
(ALL LAUGH)

02:39.967 --> 02:41.000
ALEXANDER: That's true.

02:41.100 --> 02:43.300
We were able to acquire
one of the actual jail cell windows

02:43.367 --> 02:44.600
from Alcatraz Penitentiary.

02:44.667 --> 02:45.700
We brought it in here
with us today.

02:45.767 --> 02:48.133
-Yeah, we bought it on Craigslist.
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHS)

02:48.633 --> 02:50.000
(CHUCKLES) These bars come out

02:50.067 --> 02:51.367
