02:54.200 --> 02:55.833
and see that they are in fact legit.

02:55.900 --> 02:56.933
-Here you go.
-I'll take two.

02:57.033 --> 02:59.667
-Let's show the other side.
-Show the other side of the illusion.

03:00.200 --> 03:01.367
