03:14.600 --> 03:16.633
Okay, great, hand them back
to me when you're finished.

03:17.233 --> 03:18.600
Look good?
Okay, perfect.

03:18.700 --> 03:20.267
Now I hope you guys
checked them out really well

03:20.333 --> 03:22.200
