what we're about to do,

03:22.267 --> 03:24.067
you may wish you'd looked
just a little bit harder.

03:24.200 --> 03:25.967
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHS)
-Scott's gonna place these back inside.

03:26.033 --> 03:29.000
-There goes, first off, bar number one.
-Bar number one.

03:29.233 --> 03:30.333
Bar number two.

03:30.567 --> 03:32.333
Bar number two.

03:32.433 --> 03:33.900
(CHUCKLES) Bar number three.

03:34.033 --> 03:35.967
Bar number three.

