<i>I was severely overweight.</i>
<i>I was dorkier than I am even now.</i>

10:27.800 --> 10:29.633
(LAUGHS) No, let me do it again.
I'll do it again.

10:29.700 --> 10:31.467
<i>But since then I've learned</i>
<i>how to communicate</i>

10:31.533 --> 10:33.000
<i>and connect with people.</i>

10:33.600 --> 10:35.967
<i>For me, there's absolutely</i>
<i>nothing more fulfilling</i>

10:36.033 --> 10:38.967
<i>than finding and creating</i>
<i>the moment of astonishment.</i>

10:40.000 --> 10:41.500
-(WOMAN LAUGHS)
-And you'll notice one card

10:41.567 --> 10:42.833
