26:51.167 --> 26:52.867
-That's a good thing.
-You remember your signature, right?

26:52.933 --> 26:54.133
-Yes.
-Okay, good.

26:54.733 --> 26:55.933
-ROSS: That is my signature.
-(AUDIENCE EXCLAIMS)

26:56.000 --> 26:58.233
-That was my card, ladies and gentlemen.
-(AUDIENCE APPLAUDS)

26:58.300 --> 27:00.267
Mark Calabrese!

27:01.467 --> 27:03.433
Nice job, Mark.
Come around the front here.

27:03.867 --> 27:04.967
Okay, you know how this works.

27:05.033 --> 27:06.100
Penn and Teller
are gonna talk to each other.

27:06.167 --> 27:07.800
They're gonna discuss
what they've just seen

27:07.867 --> 27:09.700
and whether they know
how it was done.

27:09.767 --> 27:10.867
Uh, let me ask you a bit
about yourself.

27:10.933 --> 27:13.100
So, you're a wrestler,
but you're kind of a real wrestler.

27:13.167 --> 27:14.700
This isn't the kind
of entertainment wrestler

27:14.767 --> 27:15.867
where it's all fixed in advance?

27:15.933 --> 27:19.967
Yeah, I mean, mixed martial arts, uh,
jujutsu, and basically beating people up

27:20.033 --> 27:21.367
