27:23.933 --> 27:26.067
-You must be in the minority.
-Yeah, I mean,

27:26.800 --> 27:28.967
-I'm still nerdy, but I like...
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHS)

27:29.033 --> 27:30.100
-you know, I like to...
-You're nerdy?

27:30.167 --> 27:31.167
If you don't like my card tricks,

27:31.267 --> 27:32.400
I just punch you
in the face and that's it.

27:32.467 --> 27:33.567
Kick me in the head,
yeah, there you go.

27:33.633 --> 27:35.067
I'm gonna like your tricks
