27:35.133 --> 27:36.167
-(ALL LAUGHING)
-Will you do me a favor?

27:36.233 --> 27:37.533
-'Cause I love your accent.
-Sure.

27:37.600 --> 27:39.300
Would you say,
"Are you looking at me?

27:39.367 --> 27:41.567
"Are you looking at me?
