27:41.667 --> 27:43.000
(ALL LAUGH)

27:43.233 --> 27:44.767
-Uh, really?
-Yeah.

27:45.567 --> 27:48.100
You looking at me?
You... You looking at me?

27:49.467 --> 27:50.933
I don't see anybody else here.
You looking at me?

27:51.000 --> 27:52.600
Wow, that's pretty good,
