29:09.067 --> 29:12.333
I think Fred Flintstone
might have said,

29:12.400 --> 29:16.367
-"Yabba, dabba, do."
-(MARK LAUGHS)

29:18.133 --> 29:22.500
Would Fred Flintstone have said,
"Yabba, dabba, do?"

29:23.267 --> 29:25.400
For a second, I thought you
just liked <i>The Flintstones...</i>

29:25.467 --> 29:27.633
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHS)
-...but he would say, Yabba, dabba, do.

29:27.700 --> 29:30.067
The rest of us feel like
we're just at a meeting

29:30.133 --> 29:32.467
of overly keen <i>Flintstones</i> fans...

29:32.533 --> 29:35.400
-(ALL LAUGH)
-...but presumably there's a code in that,

