34:30.533 --> 34:32.067
-(AUDIENCE CHEERS AND APPLAUDS)
-Thank you, Paul.

34:32.132 --> 34:34.400
-241.
-241.

34:34.467 --> 34:36.632
Give yourselves
a big round of applause!

34:37.167 --> 34:38.933
ROSS: Paul Vigil,
ladies and gentlemen.

34:39.300 --> 34:41.199
-Nice work.
-Thank you so much.

34:41.300 --> 34:42.766
-Thank you.
-Good.

34:44.067 --> 34:45.400
